      "description": "<p>S&oslash;ren Nissen &amp; Ebbe Gehl trained at Rud Rasmussen&rsquo;s workshop in Copenhagen and started their partnership in 1970 as&nbsp;<span>Furniture Designers.&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;For some years&nbsp;</span>they have been designing many pieces for international furniture brands such as the Naver Collection.</p>\r\n<p>Given their cabinetmaker backgrounds,&nbsp;<span>Timber pieces of beautiful workmanship, which only the best cabinetmakers and furniture factories have been able to make, characterise their designs.</span></p>\r\n<p>They are best known for their designs for the Naver Collection. These include an extended range of sideboards, china cabinets, coffee tables, chests of drawers and tables.</p>"
